title: Anne McCaffrey - Dragonriders of Pern 1-21, 23-24
description:
Multiple book chapters are grouped into each AAC format (m4b) iTunes-compatible audiobook file.
On your iPod and in iTunes these files will appear under Audiobooks, not Music.
As you listen, your iPod will remember your last position in the file. The next time you come back to that file, it will start where you left off!
Each audiobook file plays between 3.5 and 5 hours.
Full iTunes info, ID3, and cover art provided.
